videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo puts Julius Randle on the ground with a tricky move then explodes to the basket, making a layup and gets fouled.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis breaks Randle's ankles on way to the hoop) 2018/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis breaks Randle's ankles on way to the hoop

videos.description: Julius Randle drives down the lane, rises up and punishes the rim with a one-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Randle throws down vicious hammer) 2018/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Randle throws down vicious hammer

videos.description: The Lakers grab their own miss then Brook Lopez skies and throws down a one-handed dunk over Tyler Zeller.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lopez puts Zeller on a poster) 2018/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lopez puts Zeller on a poster

videos.description: Eric Bledsoe knocks in a 3-pointer, his fifth basket from behind the arc tonight, to extend the Bucks lead 79-65 in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Bledsoe splashes nice 3

videos.description: On three consecutive plays, Alex Caruso dishes to Ivica Zubac who each time finishes at the rim with a two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Caruso, Zubac connect for consecutive slams) 2018/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caruso, Zubac connect for consecutive slams

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma dishes it out to Brandon Ingram, who shoots a 3 from the top of the key and draws the foul on Giannis Antetokounmpo.
